    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section>
    <h2>About Atlantic Performance Horses</h2>
    <p>
      Atlantic Performance Horses was founded with a clear vision: to offer high-standard horse sourcing rooted in expertise, honesty and performance.
    </p>
    <p>
      Based in Portugal, we bring deep knowledge of the Lusitano alongside international access to high-performance sport horses — always guided by rider suitability and long-term success.
